dc_creator_sm: New Jersey. Department of Conservation and Economic Development
dc_description_s: Front of brochure features a year by year history of the Batsto family lands, furnace and glass works. There is also a small road map showing directions to Batsto. Brochure and historical village administered by the state Department of Conservation and Economic Development, Robert A. Roe, Commissioner and Kenneth H. Creveling, Director, Division of Resource Development. Arthur D. Pierce, author and Raymond N. Baker, artist.
